---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Permanent Tint & All Over Color" 
  price="Contact for pricing" 
  duration="1.5-2 hours"
  image="/images/optimized/updo-styling_800.webp"
>
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Complete Color Transformation from Roots to Ends</h2>
  
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    Transform your entire look with our all-over color service, delivering rich, vibrant, and uniform color from roots to ends. Whether you're covering gray, changing your shade completely, or enhancing your natural color, this comprehensive service ensures beautiful, long-lasting results that make a statement.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">The Power of All-Over Color</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    All-over color is the ultimate solution for complete hair transformation. Unlike touch-ups that focus on roots, this service applies fresh color to your entire head, ensuring even coverage and vibrant results. It's perfect for dramatic color changes, correcting uneven tones, or refreshing faded color throughout your hair.
  </p>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Benefits of Full Color Application</h3>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li>Complete, even color from root to tip</li>
    <li>100% gray coverage throughout</li>
    <li>Ability to dramatically change your shade</li>
    <li>Corrects uneven or patchy color</li>
    <li>Refreshes dull, faded ends</li>
    <li>Creates rich, multi-dimensional results</li>
    <li>Long-lasting color that maintains vibrancy</li>
    <li>Healthier appearance with conditioning benefits</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Ideal Candidates</h3>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-6">
    <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-4">
      <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">First-Time Color</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Virgin hair ready for transformation</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-4">
      <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Color Correction</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Fixing uneven or undesired color</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-4">
      <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Major Changes</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Going lighter or darker by multiple levels</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-4">
      <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Gray Coverage</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Complete coverage for high gray percentage</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Color Selection Process</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    Choosing the perfect shade is crucial for achieving your desired look. Melissa considers:
  </p>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li><strong>Skin tone:</strong> Warm, cool, or neutral undertones guide color selection</li>
    <li><strong>Eye color:</strong> Complementary shades that make your eyes pop</li>
    <li><strong>Lifestyle:</strong> Maintenance requirements and professional considerations</li>
    <li><strong>Personal style:</strong> Classic, trendy, or bold color choices</li>
    <li><strong>Hair condition:</strong> Current health affects color processing</li>
  </ul>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">The Application Process</h3>
  <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
    <li>Thorough consultation and color matching</li>
    <li>Strand test if needed for dramatic changes</li>
    <li>Pre-treatment to equalize porosity</li>
    <li>Systematic application starting at roots</li>
    <li>Working through mid-lengths to ends</li>
    <li>Processing time customized to your hair</li>
    <li>Gentle emulsification for even distribution</li>
    <li>Color-locking treatment and conditioning</li>
    <li>Professional finish to showcase new color</li>
  </ol>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Popular Color Transformations</h3>
  <div class="bg-[#F8F9FA] rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li><strong>Rich Brunettes:</strong> Chocolate, espresso, chestnut</li>
      <li><strong>Warm Reds:</strong> Auburn, copper, mahogany</li>
      <li><strong>Cool Blondes:</strong> Ash, pearl, platinum</li>
      <li><strong>Fashion Colors:</strong> Rose gold, violet, blue-black</li>
      <li><strong>Natural Enhancement:</strong> Deepening or brightening natural shade</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Maintaining Your New Color</h3>
  <div class="bg-[#FFDEE2] bg-opacity-20 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6">
    <h4 class="font-semibold mb-3">Color Care Essentials:</h4>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
      <li>Wait 48 hours before first wash</li>
      <li>Use color-protecting shampoo and conditioner</li>
      <li>Wash with lukewarm water, rinse with cool</li>
      <li>Deep condition weekly for color vibrancy</li>
      <li>Schedule root touch-ups every 4-6 weeks</li>
      <li>Refresh all-over color every 3-4 months</li>
      <li>Protect from sun, chlorine, and heat damage</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Investment in Confidence</h3>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
    All-over color is more than just a service – it's a complete transformation that can boost your confidence and refresh your entire look. Melissa's expertise ensures that your new color not only looks stunning on day one but continues to impress as it grows out naturally.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-[#D3E4FD] bg-opacity-20 rounded-lg p-6">
    <p class="text-gray-700 italic">
      "There's something magical about finding your perfect color. It's not just about changing your hair – it's about revealing the best version of yourself. All-over color gives you that fresh start and confidence boost we all deserve."
    </p>
  </div>
</ServiceLayout>